!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! # make image through repository packages tab visible
https://forgejo.rayka-co.com/forgejo/-/packages
Click on the package name (e.g. backup).
On the package detail page, look for an “Link to repository” or “Manage repository links” option.
Select your repo (backup) and save.
After that, the package will appear under the repo’s Packages tab.
